headline: Mizuho cuts EOG rating on lower cash margins amid weakening oil productivity
summary: Investing.com -- Mizuho downgraded EOG Resources Inc (NYSE:EOG) to Neutral from Outperform and cut its price target to $140 from $148 on declining cash margins and deteriorating well productivity.
